### ==================== ROOM ENDPOINTS ====================

### Get All Rooms
GET @api_host/api/rooms

### Get Single Room (Room ID 1)
GET @api_host/api/rooms/1

### Get Status Summary
GET @api_host/api/rooms/status/summary

### Create New Room
POST @api_host/api/rooms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 13,
  "room_number": "305",
  "floor": 3,
  "status": "vacant",
  "guest_name": null
}

### Update Room Status (Mark as Occupied)
PUT @api_host/api/rooms/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "occupied"
}

### Update Room Status (Mark as Vacant)
PUT @api_host/api/rooms/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "vacant"
}

### Update Room Status (Mark as Maintenance)
PUT @api_host/api/rooms/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "maintenance"
}

